</a> Grendl Nighthunter<BR>54th Rake<BR>Officer : <a href="http://pub52.ezboard.com/bwarcry97210"><font color=#ff0000>Cry of War</font></a><BR>Bristlebane Server<br>
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uslymmpikkins.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Slymm Pikkins</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(9/28/01 1:53:07 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: AO system requirment</span><hr size=1> Once in a while, in cities, I would lose control for a few seconds and then find myself 30 feet in front of where I stop trying to run. So far it hasnt caused me any problems (aside from navigational ones), but it is rather annoying.<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukarlek.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Karlek</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_redspot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(9/29/01 2:53:27 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.strike9.com/eq/Rakeem/fullsize/rakeem_60_y.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: AO system requirment</span><hr size=1> don't forget to slide the player visibility down to 20m or so.<br>
It helps with the city/player# induced lag enorm. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm17.showMessage?topicID=201.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm17.showMessage?topicID=197.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm17.emailToFriend?topicID=178.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm17.threadControl?topicID=178.topic><img src=http://www.evercrack.net/shpics/closeThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm17.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=178.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm17.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=178.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub35.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion">Main Lounge<option value="thesafehousecontractsbountiesjobsquestsetc">News Bulletin<option value="thesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies">Training Studio<option value="thesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers">The Back Alley<option value="thesafehousefrm13">Quests of Norrath<option value="thesafehousetherootcellar">The Root Cellar<option value="thesafehouselaboratory">Laboratory<option value="thesafehousefrm15">The Arena<option va